      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. PAW DANNY took the sit on the lead from a low draw but levelled up and led around the bend to score (34.19) at this track in a Grade 5 over 595m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Will go close again if runs up to latest. 7. ZAMBORA BLISS has hit the frame here at the last two runs, most recently finishing second beaten 5 lengths (34.37). Goes well this circuit with two wins and two minors. Ready to find winning form. 8. MAGIC LOKI missed the frame last time, finishing 5th (35.48) last time in a Grade 4/5 at The Meadows. Has won here at this journey. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Can figure in the finish. 4. PAW VINCE is a last-start placegetter worth considering.\",\"runners\":[1,7,8,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
